text: Mercer County is a county in New Jersey, United States of America. Trenton, the capital of New Jersey, is in Mercer County. As of the year 2020, 387,340 people lived in the county. Mercer County was founded in the year 1838. ==References== Category:New Jersey counties Category:1838 establishments in the United States Category:1830s establishments in New Jersey
title: Mercer County, New Jersey
